    <description>
            <![CDATA[
            <h2 class="template-title nudge">ZOE Template Framework</h2>
            
            <h3>ZOE A framework used for assembling, building and maintaining a ThemeXpert template</h3>
            <img src="../templates/tx_gravity/template_thumbnail.png" align="right" style="margin: 0px 0px 10px 10px; width:250px" />

            <h2>Overview of Our ZOE Template Framework</h2>

            <h2>Key Features</h2>

            <p>Our framework is packed with many great features that enable the rapid development of feature-rich designs with a minimum amount of effort. Check out a sampling of the features our framework brings to the table:</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Grid based layout.</li>
                <li>Tableless design and 100% css based.</li>
                <li>4 Color Theme's.</li>
                <li>Support Multiple Layout option, configurable via admin.</li>
                <li>100% Div based and no table on Joomla Core Pages.</li>
                <li>Modules suffix's built-in template for module styling.</li>
    
                <li>Support for <a href="http://cufon.shoqolate.com/generate/" rel="nofollow">Cufon</a></li>
                <li>Support for <a href="http://code.google.com/webfonts" rel="nofollow">Google Font API</a></li>
                <li>All 35 modules are fully collapsible</li>
                <li>Lightweight, modern and very fast-loading design.</li>
                <li>Joomla 1.5 Native</li>
                <li>W3C XHTML 1.0 Transitional. W3C CSS Valid</li>
                <li>Fully compatible with: IE7+, Firefox 2+, Firefox 3, Flock 0.7+, Netscape, Safari, Opera 9.5, Chrome.</li>
                <li>Delivered with “QuickStart Package”.</li>


            </ul>
            ]]>
            
</description>
